title: Serway 9th Edition Instructor Solutions Manual, Part 2
description:
Instuctor Solutions Manual - Physics for Scientists and Engineering with Modern Physics 9th edition


This text is the part 2 of the Instuctor Solutions Manual for John Serway's Physics for Scientists and Engineering with Modern Physics, 9th edition! Which is a big deal since it's not that easy to find solutions for the ninth edition. Though I was able to find only the second part, it's a big help for us students and anyone who wants to learn.

This second part consists of chapters 23-30
